Rating: 4
I enjoyed this recipe. It is a healthy appetizer with fantastic flavor. Instead of the crudites, I decided to serve the relish as a bruschetta. I took a loaf of french bread, cut slim pieces on a diagonal, sprayed all pieces with butter-flavored Pam and toasted in the oven at 350. Cooled the toast, then topped each piece with the relish...fantastic!

